Sentencas: The reduction and oxidation (redox) durability and reforming activity of MgO-NiO-YSZ composites were examined to evaluate the suitability of MgO-NiO-YSZ composites as support materials for segmented-in-series solid oxide fuel cell (SOFC) cell stacks.
Titulo: A study of electrically insulated oxide substrates for flat-tube segmented-in-series solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The MgO-NiO-YSZ composites were compared with NiO-YSZ composites.
Titulo: A study of electrically insulated oxide substrates for flat-tube segmented-in-series solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The MgO-NiO-YSZ composites showed minimal size and structural changes during redox operations at 800 degrees C and a nearly equivalent reforming activity to NiO-YSZ composites at temperatures ranging from 600 degrees C to 800 degrees C in spite of their lower Ni content.
Titulo: A study of electrically insulated oxide substrates for flat-tube segmented-in-series solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: MgO-NiO-YSZ composites are good candidates for the support materials in segmented-in-series (SIS)-type SOFC cell stacks.
Titulo: A study of electrically insulated oxide substrates for flat-tube segmented-in-series solid oxide fuel cells
